channel.title: RuneWings - by DarkCode - Devo on hold for est 3 weeks!
channel.description:
[center][img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/BANNERS/ffff.png[/img]
[url=http://www.facebook.com/pages/RuneWings/163966533620396][img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/facebook.png[/img][/url][url=http://runewings.wikispaces.com/][img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/wiki.png[/img][/url][url=http://www.youtube.com/user/runewingsrspofficial][img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/youtube.png[/img][/url]
[img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/BANNERS/INTRO.png[/img] So basically, I'm going for creativity, challenging and fun! It's all 474 and down stuff, nothing above 508! I will be adding quests, minigames and other great things for people to enjoy! Unlike most other servers, I will be having an economy and actual good skilling! You will have to work for skilling! I'm going to put up some polls for you guys to vote on and we'll see what's what. I am going to be soloing this project because I've found that when I start coding with others, I get lazy. So I'm doing it alone :) I will be using RegretScape as my base, as it's really good. I know I have been saying about a memory leak, but apparently it's not a memory leak. PK2Play told me that it was just that it used a lot of memory, and that's why the memory is out of this world.
[img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/BANNERS/UDPATES.png[/img] [code]1. Worked on Zombies - 10.18.11 2. Renamed the source - 10.20.11 3. Worked on Site - 10.20.11 4. Restored the old mage tabs - 10.21.11 5. Finished home - 10.26.11[/code]
[img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/BANNERS/GOALS.png[/img] I have high expectations for this server! [/center]
[ul][li]Basics[/li] [list] [li]Rename[/li] [li]Move Home[/li] [li]Edit Teleports[/li] [/list][/ul]
[ul][li]Zombies Minigames (Solo For Now)[/li] [list] [li]Basic Base[/li] [li]Make Waves Spawn[/li] [li]Points System[/li] [list] [li]Rewards[/li] [li]Points[/li] [/list] [/list] [list] [li]Select Zombies[/li] [li]Fix NullPointer Error[/li] [/list][/ul]
[ul][li]Make it so it doesn't use as much memory.[/li][/ul]
[ul][li]Website[/li] [list] [li]Get A New Template[/li] [list] [li]GFX Edit It[/li] [li]Edit Text[/li] [/list] [li]Hiscores[/li] [li]Auto Donations[/li] [li]Vote For Cash[/li] [/list][/ul]
[ul][li]Great Economy[/li] [list] [li]Test For Dupes (if you have names of some, please tell me what and how to do them!)[/li] [li]Look For Overly Good Drops[/li] [li]Check Prices[/li] [/list][/ul]
[center] Skills: [img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030203/runescape/images/e/e5/Prayer_Detail.PNG[/img] PRAYER [img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030203/runescape/images/e/e5/Prayer_Detail.PNG[/img] 1. Handle differently 2. Add special graveyard for bonus xp
[img]http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030123/runescape/images/8/84/Crafting_detail.png[/img]Crafting[img]http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030123/runescape/images/8/84/Crafting_detail.png[/img] 1. Handle Differently 2. Add pottery making
[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100404194836/runescape/images/4/42/Farming_detail.png[/img]Farming (only herbs for now)[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100404194836/runescape/images/4/42/Farming_detail.png[/img] 1. Seed, object and harvesting 2. Raking, Watering, Dibbing, and possibly compost 3. Magic Secateurs for bonus herbs
[img]http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030141/runescape/images/e/e4/Fishing_logo_detail.png[/img]Fishing[img]http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030141/runescape/images/e/e4/Fishing_logo_detail.png[/img] 1. Handle Differently
[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030134/runescape/images/4/43/Fm_symbol.PNG[/img]Firemaking[img]http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030134/runescape/images/4/43/Fm_symbol.PNG[/img] 1. Handle Differently
[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030223/runescape/images/6/63/Wc_symbol.PNG[/img]Woodcutting[img]http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030223/runescape/images/6/63/Wc_symbol.PNG[/img] 1. Handle Differently 2. Nests
[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030156/runescape/images/8/80/Mining_Detail.PNG[/img]Mining[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100917030156/runescape/images/8/80/Mining_Detail.PNG[/img] 1. Handle Differently 2. Add new ores
[img]http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103032428/runescape/images/4/48/Slayer_Detail.PNG[/img]Slayer[img]http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103032428/runescape/images/4/48/Slayer_Detail.PNG[/img] 1. Handle Differently 2. Add new monsters
[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103041122/runescape/images/4/4b/Herblore_detail.png[/img]Herblore[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103041122/runescape/images/4/4b/Herblore_detail.png[/img] 1. Handle Differently 2. Add more potions
[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103040802/runescape/images/0/0c/Fletching.png[/img]Fletching[img]http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20101103040802/runescape/images/0/0c/Fletching.png[/img] 1. Handle Differently [img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/BANNERS/media.png[/img] Got a new site. Gunna work with it soon :)
[img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/header1.png[/img] Before and After: [img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/b4.png[/img][img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/now.png[/img]
[img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/BANNERS/CONCLUSION.png[/img] I'm also planning on adding quests among lots of other things, but for now, those are my priorities. Yes, I know I didn't rename or anything and all you noobs out there are probably like "0mFG!?!!?!? L33CHeRz!!!!". So if you are like that, [shadow=black,left][u][i][b]FUCK OFF[/b][/i][/u][/shadow], I've been working on my Zombies Minigame for a long while now and haven't found the time to really work on small stuff like that... Please, comment and tell me what you think!
[img]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/18329363/BANNERS/SUPPORTERS.png[/img] PK2Play for helping me out with the memory leak and other things. People who originally tried to help me with the null pointer error (forget names atm, I'll look em up later). Wolfy and Kronixfor supporting me and encouraging me. imsuperman05 for helping me set up eclipse and other things :)

More shit is allocated on server initialization from the clipping system…
